Title: API: fixing the list group endpoints for host_group, contact_group and service_group
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1612253498
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

In the previous version, the list group endpoints for host_group,
contact_group and service_group returned a 500 error when called.
This werk fixes this behaviour.
